    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>清理并放松</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spilled! 是一款短小的游戏，没有错误的玩法方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在大约一个小时内完成它。放松，花多少时间都行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/8c61d449f0e738339bc8c2cae57d28a0.poster.avif?t=1750688351\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/8c61d449f0e738339bc8c2cae57d28a0.webm?t=1750688351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/8c61d449f0e738339bc8c2cae57d28a0.mp4?t=1750688351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>回收油并升级你的船</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为下一个区域准备好你的船！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/b9f1251925f16c1c630a0d538692d17d.poster.avif?t=1750688351\" width=600 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/b9f1251925f16c1c630a0d538692d17d.webm?t=1750688351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/b9f1251925f16c1c630a0d538692d17d.mp4?t=1750688351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索新的区域，面对更大的油污和新的垃圾种类</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越不同的生态区，推动塑料到回收中心，扑灭火灾等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/ab2fda8b13cadd2f18ae782eed139e12.avif?t=1750688351\" width=600 height=371 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>找到并拯救可爱的动物们</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中有16只动物等着你来拯救！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/3b2d805147d8016a5024325a29b76fba.poster.avif?t=1750688351\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/3b2d805147d8016a5024325a29b76fba.webm?t=1750688351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/3b2d805147d8016a5024325a29b76fba.mp4?t=1750688351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大约1小时的游戏时间。随时可以使用关卡选择器返回放松。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清理、回收、赚取金币并升级你的船以应对下一个区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8个可供探索的区域，每个区域都更大，油污和垃圾种类也更多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中穿越不同的生态区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中找到并拯救16只不同的动物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👩‍💻 关于开发者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你好！我叫Lente。我在2022年底开始制作Spilled!。这是我的第一次商业发布。[/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我暂停了学业，买了一艘小船来住。这降低了我的生活成本，并让我能够全身心投入到Spilled!的制作中。[/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当我的储蓄用尽时，我成功地发起了Kickstarter，并一直支持到发布！我非常高兴能够追随自己的梦想。希望你会喜欢Spilled!。[/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/i][/i]<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240080/extras/65e3a08ae6297798ffe89467e412d7de.avif?t=1750688351\" width=600 height=153 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/i][/i] </p></p></p></i></p>",
